OrderWise-Agent
Copyright 2026 UCloud

OrderWise-Agent is licensed under Apache License 2.0.

OrderWise-Agent is a derivative work based on Open-AutoGLM (developed by Zhipu AI),
specialized for food delivery price comparison. It extends Open-AutoGLM with parallel execution,
structured price extraction, MongoDB integration for asynchronous task processing, Model Context
Protocol (MCP) interface for price comparison with synchronous human intervention, and enhanced
device management.

